## null_resource

### Basic Usage

```hcl
resource "null_resource" "trigger" {
  triggers = {
    always = timestamp()
  }

  provisioner "local-exec" {
    command = "echo 'Running ${timestamp()}'"
  }
}
```

### With depends_on

```hcl
resource "null_resource" "wait_for_db" {
  depends_on = [oci_database_autonomous_database.adb]

  triggers = {
    db_state = oci_database_autonomous_database.adb.state
  }

  provisioner "local-exec" {
    command = "echo 'DB ready'"
  }
}
```

### Use Cases

- Trigger on any change
- Wait for resource ready
- Run scripts after provision

### Modern Alternative

- terraform_data resource (1.5+)
